WEBVTT

00:15.460 --> 00:19.960
♪During the dark night♪

00:20.100 --> 00:22.750
♪A guiding light♪

00:23.260 --> 00:25.050
♪Just like you♪

00:25.460 --> 00:29.750
♪Makes life turn bright♪

00:30.330 --> 00:35.180
♪Breaking free from darkness♪

00:35.400 --> 00:38.880
♪You gave me strength♪

00:39.230 --> 00:41.780
♪Running for truth♪

00:41.800 --> 00:45.850
♪I find my path♪

00:46.600 --> 00:50.580
♪Drawing on the hope♪

00:51.200 --> 00:54.580
♪That you render me♪

00:55.130 --> 00:58.010
♪In this long journey♪

00:58.260 --> 01:01.680
♪I run on lightly♪

01:19.180 --> 01:22.980
[Reborn]
[Adapted from Qiang Yu's work, Reborn]

01:23.650 --> 01:24.840
You're different from her.

01:27.130 --> 01:28.050
You're

01:29.450 --> 01:30.560
the pure type.

01:30.930 --> 01:32.370
I actually understood
what your sister was thinking

01:32.370 --> 01:33.240
back then.

01:33.450 --> 01:35.370
She was protecting you.

01:36.080 --> 01:37.370
You were so young.

01:38.479 --> 01:41.200
She didn't want you to have
anything to do with someone like me.

01:41.360 --> 01:42.289
But it didn't matter

01:42.729 --> 01:45.360
because now we know each other,
and it's not too late.

01:47.520 --> 01:49.450
And look at you,

01:50.090 --> 01:52.130
all grown up

01:52.640 --> 01:53.640
and beautiful!

01:53.640 --> 01:54.360
Don't touch me!

01:54.360 --> 01:55.360
So what if I'm touching you?

01:55.610 --> 01:56.170
Stay away from me!

01:56.170 --> 01:56.720
No!

01:56.970 --> 01:57.530
I'll go further than that.

01:57.530 --> 01:58.080
Don't touch me!

01:58.120 --> 01:58.490
Hey, what are you doing?

01:58.680 --> 01:59.759
From now on, you're mine.

01:59.759 --> 01:59.970
Hei!

01:59.970 --> 02:01.640
You'll be paying back
what your sister owed me.

02:01.640 --> 02:02.760
Someone smashed our car.

02:02.910 --> 02:03.640
Who did that?

02:04.350 --> 02:05.170
Who smashed my car?

02:35.550 --> 02:36.350
Don't worry.

02:36.510 --> 02:37.510
They won't catch up.

02:38.710 --> 02:39.950
Did you smash his car?

02:44.370 --> 02:45.170
Qiao Qingyu,

02:45.400 --> 02:46.370
I don't understand

02:46.680 --> 02:48.970
why you're involved with those rascals.

02:49.400 --> 02:50.920
But I believe

02:51.250 --> 02:52.890
they won't let you off so easily.

02:52.970 --> 02:53.970
Thank you for reminding me.

02:54.250 --> 02:55.320
I'll be careful.

02:58.810 --> 03:01.480
All right. You can call me Mumu
from now on,

03:01.890 --> 03:02.890
and I'll call you Qingyu.

03:05.320 --> 03:05.810
Mumu.

03:07.070 --> 03:09.620
[A Dance Tribute to Qiao Beiyu]

03:52.650 --> 03:54.120
Stand up. Let me fix your costume.

04:02.930 --> 04:04.970
All right, it's done. Shall we start?

04:13.810 --> 04:14.650
Do you like them?

04:34.470 --> 04:39.390
[Episode 7]
[Cries from Nanqiao Village]

04:40.650 --> 04:42.159
Keep this.
We hope to see you again soon.

04:42.430 --> 04:43.000
Are you full?

04:43.270 --> 04:43.440
Yes.

04:43.790 --> 04:44.190
Go get the car.

04:46.630 --> 04:47.390
Check, please.

04:47.550 --> 04:47.950
All right.

04:48.990 --> 04:49.630
Which table?

04:49.950 --> 04:50.430
Table 4.

04:50.430 --> 04:51.510
Table 4, I see.

04:52.750 --> 04:54.510
Three servings of pork chop noodles.
That's 36 yuan.

04:56.550 --> 04:58.190
Here's 100 yuan. Keep the change.

04:58.550 --> 04:59.190
That won't do.

05:01.750 --> 05:02.350
It's fine.

05:03.430 --> 05:04.990
Is Qiao Beiyu your daughter?

05:07.250 --> 05:08.680
She was my girlfriend.

05:08.880 --> 05:11.530
So you're practically my mother-in-law.

05:12.280 --> 05:13.880
Taking care of your noodle house

05:14.280 --> 05:15.120
is something I should do, right?

05:15.120 --> 05:16.600
No need to give me back
the change, right?

05:17.680 --> 05:18.650
Is this a mistake?

05:18.650 --> 05:20.530
I... I have no idea
who you're talking about.

05:20.680 --> 05:21.930
I don't need your money. Please leave.

05:23.430 --> 05:24.490
I'm an adult.

05:25.350 --> 05:26.650
How could I dine and dash?

05:27.070 --> 05:28.550
It's fine if you don't know her.

05:29.550 --> 05:30.990
You have another daughter, right?

05:33.630 --> 05:35.630
Why isn't she here?

05:36.710 --> 05:37.790
Please take the money.

05:37.950 --> 05:38.830
I'll come back another day.

05:42.390 --> 05:43.150
Make ways.

05:44.390 --> 05:45.110
Madam.

05:45.950 --> 05:46.470
Hey.

05:46.870 --> 05:47.590
Madam.

05:49.790 --> 05:50.630
Jeez.

05:51.110 --> 05:52.030
We're neighbors.

05:52.030 --> 05:53.590
I'm just showing care.

05:53.590 --> 05:54.670
Why are you ignoring me?

05:57.350 --> 05:58.590
Don't get her wrong, Ma.

05:58.830 --> 05:59.950
She's not ignoring you.

06:00.630 --> 06:01.430
How about this?

06:01.430 --> 06:03.310
This bowl of noodles is on the house.

06:04.590 --> 06:06.070
I can't let you do that.

06:06.350 --> 06:07.670
No, it's nothing.

06:26.970 --> 06:27.770
Is it acting up again?

06:28.210 --> 06:29.010
I'm good.

06:30.480 --> 06:31.570
I'll massage it for you
when we get home.

06:36.210 --> 06:38.360
Don't let Qingyu come here.

06:40.010 --> 06:41.770
Don't make a fuss about it.

06:42.330 --> 06:44.530
Those thugs are just trying to scare us.

06:45.800 --> 06:46.480
Besides,

06:46.800 --> 06:49.010
we can't manage the shop alone.

06:49.400 --> 06:50.400
Absolutely not.

06:52.770 --> 06:54.240
I'll see what I can do.

06:55.330 --> 06:55.770
Also,

06:56.770 --> 06:57.720
don't let Qingyu know about this.

06:58.590 --> 07:01.640
[Qiao's Handmade Noodle House]

07:51.070 --> 07:51.710
Qingyu,

07:52.190 --> 07:53.350
we've got a guest.

07:56.070 --> 07:56.590
Qian Huan.

07:56.630 --> 07:56.990
Yes.

07:57.190 --> 07:58.750
It's our family shop.

07:58.950 --> 08:00.950
If you're tired, just let me know.
Don't worry.

08:01.670 --> 08:02.750
If you want to eat

08:02.750 --> 08:03.840
or need anything, just let me know.

08:04.030 --> 08:04.970
The department store is around here.

08:05.150 --> 08:06.090
We can go shopping anytime.

08:06.390 --> 08:08.530
Don't worry about me.
I have got everything I need.

08:08.710 --> 08:09.920
Look, I even brought my foot basin.

08:10.750 --> 08:10.970
Have some water.

08:11.270 --> 08:11.720
Sure.

08:13.230 --> 08:13.970
Uncle Lusheng, Aunt Fanghao,

08:14.430 --> 08:15.570
your place is big.

08:15.830 --> 08:16.130
Well, no.

08:16.990 --> 08:17.800
The apartments in the city

08:17.990 --> 08:19.920
are not as comfortable
as the old houses back home.

08:20.110 --> 08:21.570
The countryside can't match the city.

08:21.750 --> 08:23.210
Everything in big cities is pricey.

08:23.950 --> 08:24.890
In my factory dorm,

08:25.070 --> 08:26.360
we have eight people
sharing a single room,

08:26.630 --> 08:28.480
with shared bathrooms and toilets.

08:28.710 --> 08:29.240
Oh.

08:31.390 --> 08:33.330
You're back. Let me introduce you
to each other.

08:33.630 --> 08:36.130
This is Qingyu and Yu.

08:36.630 --> 08:38.360
This is your cousin, Qiao Huan.

08:39.549 --> 08:42.039
She's Uncle Pengfei's daughter.

08:42.990 --> 08:44.010
Go on, say hello.

08:44.670 --> 08:45.690
- Hi, Qiao Huan.
- Hi, Qiao Huan.

08:46.190 --> 08:47.720
You were childhood playmates.

08:47.910 --> 08:48.600
Don't you recognize each other now?

08:48.910 --> 08:49.770
Hi, Qingyu, Jinyu.

08:49.950 --> 08:50.450
Have a seat.

08:50.670 --> 08:51.010
Come. Have a seat.

08:51.870 --> 08:54.360
Qiao Huan's factory closed down,

08:54.550 --> 08:55.160
so

08:55.510 --> 08:56.970
she came here to help us out.

08:57.470 --> 08:58.280
So starting today,

08:58.470 --> 09:00.010
you don't have to
go to the shop anymore.

09:00.470 --> 09:01.890
Come straight home after school.

09:02.190 --> 09:03.480
I'll bring dinner back for you.

09:03.670 --> 09:04.240
Really?

09:04.710 --> 09:05.330
Hooray, Mom!

09:07.390 --> 09:07.650
Huan,

09:07.990 --> 09:09.600
I'm sorry you have to

09:09.790 --> 09:10.970
make do with the sofa tonight.

09:11.190 --> 09:11.600
Sure.

09:11.790 --> 09:12.450
Tomorrow...

09:12.630 --> 09:13.360
What's going on?

09:13.550 --> 09:14.210
You can move over
once everything is set up.

09:14.390 --> 09:15.920
I have no idea.

09:27.280 --> 09:28.240
Mom, what are you doing?

09:28.570 --> 09:30.280
I'm throwing all these clothes away.

09:30.770 --> 09:32.210
You don't need them at school.

09:32.800 --> 09:34.130
Why are you throwing them away?

09:35.600 --> 09:36.650
They are too fancy.

09:37.330 --> 09:38.770
Not at all.

09:38.770 --> 09:40.130
What am I supposed to wear
if you throw them all away?

09:40.770 --> 09:42.210
You have your school uniform.

09:44.800 --> 09:45.330
This one.

09:46.690 --> 09:47.400
Cashmere.

09:47.600 --> 09:48.360
It's new.

09:48.360 --> 09:50.130
It's been two years.
You haven't got a chance to wear it.

09:50.890 --> 09:52.010
Good. It can keep you warm.

10:01.290 --> 10:02.090
What?

10:02.930 --> 10:04.930
Something seems off about Mom,
don't you think?

10:05.930 --> 10:08.360
There's nothing to be surprised.

10:08.880 --> 10:11.210
It'd be strange if she acted normal.

10:18.520 --> 10:20.840
Qian Huan, my mom said

10:20.840 --> 10:23.120
you used to work at a clothing factory
in Huanzhou.

10:23.600 --> 10:24.410
Yes.

10:24.690 --> 10:26.880
I started working when I was your age.

10:27.210 --> 10:30.330
It's been four to five years.

10:30.600 --> 10:31.840
Didn't you go to school?

10:32.570 --> 10:33.720
I'm not like you.

10:33.720 --> 10:35.480
I'm not cut out for studying.

10:35.760 --> 10:37.450
In Nanqiao Village,

10:37.450 --> 10:38.480
girls who graduate from junior high

10:38.480 --> 10:39.330
either get married immediately

10:39.330 --> 10:41.090
or leave to work
to support their families.

10:41.290 --> 10:43.000
The only girl who got support
from their parents to finish senior high

10:43.000 --> 10:44.240
and associate degree program

10:44.240 --> 10:45.090
was Beiyu,

10:45.090 --> 10:46.360
but she turned out worse than us.

10:49.840 --> 10:51.760
Qingyu, I wasn't thinking.

10:51.760 --> 10:53.000
Don't take it personally.

10:53.520 --> 10:54.330
It's fine.

10:54.840 --> 10:57.170
There are many job opportunities
in Huanzhou.

10:57.410 --> 10:59.240
Why would you work at our noodle house?

11:00.000 --> 11:01.410
Easy job, high pay.

11:01.410 --> 11:03.050
Besides, we're relatives.

11:03.050 --> 11:04.840
And Aunt Fanghao said
she desperately needed help.

11:04.840 --> 11:06.290
I thought I could help,

11:06.290 --> 11:07.090
so I came.

11:10.170 --> 11:12.050
So your factory didn't close down.

11:12.170 --> 11:13.410
It's because my mom asked you to come.

11:15.570 --> 11:16.640
Right.

11:16.880 --> 11:18.330
The factory did shut down.

11:18.570 --> 11:19.840
I'm so forgetful.

11:25.170 --> 11:28.930
Qingyu, your parents
really care about you.

12:01.840 --> 12:03.340
[It's getting colder.
Baby, make sure you bundle up.]

12:03.340 --> 12:04.840
[Or else I'll be worried about you.]

12:04.840 --> 12:05.640
Qingyu,

12:05.720 --> 12:07.090
is the thug at the gate

12:07.090 --> 12:08.360
really your boyfriend?

12:27.970 --> 12:28.810
You're a man.

12:28.810 --> 12:30.000
Why are you drinking something so pink?

12:30.810 --> 12:32.240
It's sweet and pretty.
Don't you like it?

12:32.240 --> 12:32.570
Here.

12:32.690 --> 12:33.170
What flavor is this?

12:33.170 --> 12:34.090
Pink and green.

12:34.930 --> 12:35.450
What a good match.

12:36.320 --> 12:38.040
[Huanzhou High School]

12:40.520 --> 12:41.410
What's wrong with her?

12:41.970 --> 12:43.050
She's in trouble.

12:45.640 --> 12:46.450
What's going on?

12:48.930 --> 12:49.810
What happened?

12:50.600 --> 12:51.930
She's bold enough

12:52.000 --> 12:53.090
to mess with Hei.

12:53.240 --> 12:54.410
Hei's a thug.

12:54.450 --> 12:55.840
He's infamously ruthless.

12:57.170 --> 12:58.050
She's in for it.

13:30.170 --> 13:31.170
Why is it you?

13:32.360 --> 13:33.520
Who else could it be?

13:37.120 --> 13:38.450
Stop looking around. Just the two of us.

13:38.600 --> 13:40.050
Aren't you heading home? Go on.

13:40.640 --> 13:41.640
Do you live around here?

13:41.810 --> 13:42.880
I haven't seen you before.

13:45.090 --> 13:45.970
I'm meeting Wang Mumu.

14:38.290 --> 14:39.090
Urgh.

14:39.450 --> 14:40.840
This house is quite run-down.

14:40.840 --> 14:42.970
I'm so sick of this water heater
breaking down.

14:43.210 --> 14:44.000
We should

14:44.000 --> 14:45.570
get a new one.

14:46.120 --> 14:47.480
And when we move out,

14:47.480 --> 14:49.330
are we going to take it with us?

14:49.600 --> 14:51.450
Dad and Mom work hard to make a living.

14:51.450 --> 14:52.640
We need to save money.

14:52.760 --> 14:54.330
Don't spend as you wish.

14:56.170 --> 14:56.720
Qiao Jinyu.

14:57.290 --> 14:57.810
What?

14:58.050 --> 14:58.690
Come here.

15:03.480 --> 15:05.360
He Feihai told me

15:05.690 --> 15:07.930
Qiao Beiyu ran away

15:08.290 --> 15:10.410
from Nanqiao Village to Shunyun.

15:11.360 --> 15:12.520
Did you know about this?

15:14.520 --> 15:15.880
I...

15:18.090 --> 15:19.410
I knew.

15:19.880 --> 15:21.120
Why don't I remember anything about it?

15:22.520 --> 15:24.640
Dad and Mom didn't let me tell you.

15:26.240 --> 15:28.810
It was a freezing day,

15:29.340 --> 15:32.500
dark and gloomy,
with heavy snow on the way.

15:33.290 --> 15:34.880
I saw her on my way home.

15:54.240 --> 15:55.050
Yu.

16:03.760 --> 16:05.690
Dad, Mom.

16:08.690 --> 16:10.330
I don't want to go back
to Nanqiao Village anymore.

16:11.880 --> 16:13.360
I don't want to sit for NCEE.

16:14.290 --> 16:17.050
I want to stay here in Shunyun with you.

16:19.840 --> 16:21.570
I can help out at the shop.

16:22.410 --> 16:24.090
I won't be a nuisance.

16:24.840 --> 16:27.000
But you have to finish high school.

16:27.690 --> 16:29.810
Aren't you planning to apply
to the dance academy?

16:30.410 --> 16:31.570
I don't want to study anymore.

16:33.050 --> 16:34.570
As long as I can be with you,

16:34.720 --> 16:36.000
I'm fine with quitting school.

16:37.930 --> 16:38.760
Beiyu,

16:39.970 --> 16:40.970
what about your future

16:42.360 --> 16:43.640
if you quit school now?

16:43.760 --> 16:45.170
Have you not heard about this?

16:45.290 --> 16:47.360
University graduates
are everywhere nowadays.

16:47.690 --> 16:51.090
If you can't graduate from high school,

16:52.000 --> 16:52.880
it'd be so embarrassing

16:53.880 --> 16:54.810
if people found out.

16:54.810 --> 16:56.000
I'm not afraid of that.

16:56.000 --> 16:57.480
But I am.

17:08.000 --> 17:10.839
Beiyu, listen to me.

17:12.720 --> 17:16.050
You must finish your studies, all right?

17:17.050 --> 17:18.640
I understand you're upset.

17:19.000 --> 17:19.930
I know you...

17:21.930 --> 17:23.089
Since you were a kid,

17:24.050 --> 17:25.240
I haven't been around you

17:26.839 --> 17:28.240
and have put you through a lot.

17:28.880 --> 17:30.880
But you see,

17:31.840 --> 17:33.410
everyone has tough times in their lives,

17:34.120 --> 17:34.930
right?

17:35.690 --> 17:37.290
Sometimes, you just have to

17:38.120 --> 17:40.520
endure and push through.

17:40.600 --> 17:41.640
You'll get over it.

17:44.760 --> 17:46.000
Think it through.

17:46.210 --> 17:48.120
Take your future seriously,

17:48.120 --> 17:48.720
right?

17:51.970 --> 17:53.570
Your mom's right.

17:54.760 --> 17:56.810
Everything will be all right
once you get into the university.

18:01.360 --> 18:02.210
Dad, Mom!

18:02.210 --> 18:03.640
Why is no one watching the shop?

18:03.640 --> 18:05.170
- Okay.
- Coming.

19:12.220 --> 19:13.100
After that,

19:13.720 --> 19:16.370
I didn't hear about her running away.

19:16.800 --> 19:17.970
She didn't run

19:18.410 --> 19:20.610
because she knew no one would save her.

19:21.800 --> 19:23.170
Back then, if...

19:23.410 --> 19:24.370
Back then,

19:24.370 --> 19:26.130
we were just kids.

19:26.690 --> 19:27.890
Even if we knew,

19:27.930 --> 19:29.040
what could we do?

19:31.930 --> 19:33.080
Where are you going?

19:33.520 --> 19:34.560
I'm going to ask Dad and Mom

19:34.560 --> 19:35.970
why they didn't help Qiao Beiyu?

19:36.520 --> 19:37.410
Hey, you...

19:38.000 --> 19:39.370
Don't say I told you this.

19:39.800 --> 19:40.410
Hey!

19:40.410 --> 19:41.650
[Qiao's Handmade Noodle House]
What are you doing?

19:41.650 --> 19:42.610
Call the police.

19:42.800 --> 19:43.970
Call the police now.

19:44.850 --> 19:46.000
Call the police.

19:46.170 --> 19:46.800
Call the police. Quick!

19:55.610 --> 19:57.210
Get your daughter here.

19:59.930 --> 20:01.850
Hei, well...

20:02.890 --> 20:05.610
Don't be mad with her.
She's just a girl.

20:08.280 --> 20:09.890
Nonsense.

20:09.890 --> 20:11.760
It was Qiao Beiyu

20:11.760 --> 20:14.320
who hooked up with other men
behind my back.

20:14.690 --> 20:16.170
She cheated on me.

20:17.000 --> 20:18.560
She embarrassed me.

20:19.720 --> 20:21.130
She owed me this, didn't she?

20:22.610 --> 20:25.280
So her sister should repay
what she owed me.

20:25.720 --> 20:27.240
Isn't that the way it has to be?

20:27.240 --> 20:28.370
It has nothing to do with her.

20:32.210 --> 20:33.240
Do you have garlic?

20:34.720 --> 20:35.370
Garlic.

20:35.480 --> 20:36.850
Yes, we do.

20:41.520 --> 20:43.850
If my child did something wrong,

20:43.850 --> 20:45.520
I'll apologize for her.

20:45.520 --> 20:48.170
But this has nothing to do with Qingyu.

20:50.320 --> 20:51.040
Hey.

20:52.320 --> 20:53.480
Don't

20:53.480 --> 20:55.040
play the victim.

20:55.040 --> 20:57.850
I just want to date your daughter.

20:57.850 --> 20:59.210
It's not like I'd eat her.

21:00.520 --> 21:01.450
Besides,

21:01.760 --> 21:04.970
it was Qiao Qingyu
who reached out to me.

21:04.970 --> 21:06.040
She was the one who made the first move.

21:06.040 --> 21:06.970
This is impossible!

21:07.850 --> 21:09.560
I guess you haven't known yet.

21:09.560 --> 21:12.480
Your daughter asked around about Hei.

21:12.670 --> 21:13.520
Doesn't that mean
she's interested in him?

21:13.520 --> 21:14.210
Nonsense!

21:14.520 --> 21:16.720
Well, get your daughter here.

21:16.970 --> 21:18.760
Just ask her and you'll get your answer.

21:21.170 --> 21:22.000
So spicy.

21:24.630 --> 21:25.070
Ah!

21:25.610 --> 21:26.280
What are you doing?

21:37.610 --> 21:38.520
No...

21:38.850 --> 21:39.690
I'm sorry.

21:39.690 --> 21:41.000
So sorry.

21:44.310 --> 21:45.280
Here you are.

21:47.040 --> 21:47.930
The police are here.

21:49.450 --> 21:50.890
Hei, should we go?

21:56.950 --> 21:57.890
It's over. You should go.

21:58.710 --> 21:59.610
It's over now. Just go.

21:59.790 --> 22:00.350
Leave.

22:18.040 --> 22:18.690
Qingyu.

22:22.480 --> 22:24.890
Be careful when you're out alone.

22:27.720 --> 22:30.210
Stay away from those thugs.

22:32.610 --> 22:33.650
Did I warn you this before?

22:35.760 --> 22:36.800
They claimed

22:37.240 --> 22:38.760
you approached them.

22:41.720 --> 22:42.650
What were you up to?

22:45.280 --> 22:46.410
I just wanted to find out

22:47.280 --> 22:49.080
who caused Qiao Beiyu's death.

22:52.080 --> 22:54.210
She brought shame to herself.
No one else is to blame.

22:54.930 --> 22:55.560
Seriously?

22:56.280 --> 22:57.480
She's already gone.

22:57.480 --> 22:58.760
What more do you want to know?

22:59.210 --> 23:00.410
Don't keep digging!

23:00.410 --> 23:01.520
Exposing everything

23:01.520 --> 23:03.080
will destroy our family's

23:03.080 --> 23:04.320
already damaged reputation.

23:04.650 --> 23:05.970
Did you say that to Qiao Beiyu

23:05.970 --> 23:07.210
when she

23:07.410 --> 23:08.930
fled Nanqiao Village for Shunyun?

23:09.000 --> 23:09.890
What did you say?

23:11.520 --> 23:12.610
It was cold.

23:13.650 --> 23:15.130
Qiao Beiyu ran all the way here

23:15.130 --> 23:16.280
to seek your help,

23:17.210 --> 23:18.760
but what did you do?

23:19.320 --> 23:21.480
You knew she was bullied
in Nanqiao Village.

23:21.520 --> 23:22.170
You knew

23:22.170 --> 23:23.690
what she went through.

23:24.890 --> 23:25.970
But you didn't save her.

23:26.170 --> 23:27.210
What nonsense are you talking about?

23:27.760 --> 23:29.850
I was going to ask
why you didn't save her,

23:30.170 --> 23:32.040
but I know the answer now.

23:34.560 --> 23:36.130
Because you're too selfish.

23:36.130 --> 23:37.240
Because you think Beiyu's life

23:37.240 --> 23:38.690
was less important than your pride!

23:38.690 --> 23:39.370
Qing!

23:39.410 --> 23:39.760
Go away!

24:01.480 --> 24:02.560
Are you not angry

24:02.690 --> 24:03.450
with what they say about you?

24:03.650 --> 24:04.370
Qiao Beiyu,

24:04.370 --> 24:05.690
is what they're saying true?

24:05.890 --> 24:07.450
Are you really like what they say?

24:07.650 --> 24:09.610
If you tell me it's not true,
I'll believe you.

24:10.970 --> 24:12.370
Qiao Beiyu, answer me.

24:12.610 --> 24:13.280
Qiao Beiyu.

24:17.690 --> 24:18.720
What if it's true?

24:20.520 --> 24:22.370
If you don't want to end up like me,

24:23.650 --> 24:25.240
stay away from me.

26:36.800 --> 26:37.480
What?

26:38.450 --> 26:41.240
I came to remind you
that today is Mr. Ming's birthday.

26:43.370 --> 26:44.320
What does it have to do with me?

26:45.690 --> 26:47.930
It does with me.

26:48.080 --> 26:50.210
My mom is his regular patient,

26:50.720 --> 26:53.210
so I'd like to thank him

26:53.210 --> 26:54.650
on his birthday.

26:57.000 --> 26:58.280
I have practice after school.

26:58.480 --> 27:00.000
Bring this to him for me.

27:01.130 --> 27:01.800
Thanks a bunch.

27:04.690 --> 27:06.930
If you're not free or don't want to,

27:08.370 --> 27:09.210
throw it away.

27:09.210 --> 27:11.280
I'll throw it away.
Don't think I won't dare.

27:25.650 --> 27:26.800
Notify the blood bank

27:27.170 --> 27:28.520
to prepare four units
of red blood cells,

27:28.610 --> 27:29.480
400 ml of plasma,

27:29.480 --> 27:30.850
and ten units of cryoprecipitate.

27:33.890 --> 27:34.520
Okay.

27:34.720 --> 27:36.720
The leukemia patient
is in critical condition.

27:37.080 --> 27:37.690
Ming Sheng.

27:40.450 --> 27:41.610
A critically ill patient
has just been admitted

27:41.610 --> 27:42.720
for emergency surgery.

27:44.080 --> 27:45.040
Wait in his room.

27:45.040 --> 27:46.040
I'll have him come over
once the surgery is done.

27:46.040 --> 27:47.170
Just stay here.

28:17.170 --> 28:18.440
[Diagnostic Criteria for Hepatobiliary
and Pancreatic Surgical Diseases]

28:55.170 --> 28:56.650
Connect the patient to the ECG monitor.

28:57.210 --> 28:58.850
Make sure to pay attention
to their vitals and urine output.

28:59.210 --> 29:00.170
But remember this.

29:00.170 --> 29:01.890
The patient has
their right liver removed.

29:02.520 --> 29:03.410
Do remember to inform
the family about this.

29:03.410 --> 29:04.610
All right, Dr. Ming.

29:05.080 --> 29:07.210
This is the standard procedure.
There will be no mistakes.

29:08.760 --> 29:09.760
You should get off work now.

29:10.760 --> 29:12.450
It's fine. I need to head to the ICU.

29:13.610 --> 29:15.040
Have you forgotten what day it is?

29:17.000 --> 29:17.650
Dr. Ming.

29:17.650 --> 29:18.320
Yes.

29:21.280 --> 29:22.080
What day is it?

29:23.170 --> 29:25.320
Today's your birthday. Did you forget?

29:27.560 --> 29:28.480
Ming Sheng is here.

29:29.790 --> 29:30.990
He prepared a birthday cake for you.

29:30.990 --> 29:31.730
He's waiting for you in your room.

29:32.520 --> 29:33.130
Go on.

29:35.890 --> 29:36.320
Go.

30:38.720 --> 30:39.760
It's getting colder.

30:39.850 --> 30:41.890
Aunt Fanghao told me
to get a thick blanket.

30:43.240 --> 30:45.280
Life in the city is pleasant,

30:45.480 --> 30:47.850
even the winters are mild.

30:50.760 --> 30:53.080
By the way, have you heard about that?

30:53.800 --> 30:55.850
Aunt Qin is dead.

30:58.480 --> 30:59.450
What has happened?

31:00.930 --> 31:02.560
After she was taken out of the fire,

31:02.560 --> 31:04.080
she had been in a bad condition.

31:04.370 --> 31:06.000
She was hospitalized for a while,

31:06.000 --> 31:07.040
but her condition didn't improve.

31:07.040 --> 31:08.890
The expenses were so much higher

31:09.210 --> 31:10.450
that Uncle Jiangsheng had no choice

31:10.520 --> 31:12.690
but to bring her home.

31:12.800 --> 31:14.720
She struggled for a while more,

31:14.890 --> 31:16.480
but eventually,
she couldn't hold on anymore.

31:18.280 --> 31:21.560
Frankly, she's probably at peace now.

31:23.370 --> 31:25.720
Aunt Qin was pretty and educated.

31:26.000 --> 31:27.800
It's a shame she had a terrible fate.

31:28.930 --> 31:30.170
Why would someone like her

31:30.170 --> 31:31.890
marry into Nanqiao Village?

31:33.210 --> 31:34.370
My mom said

31:34.480 --> 31:36.370
Aunt Qin had a younger brother.

31:36.850 --> 31:39.280
Her parents married her off

31:39.280 --> 31:41.720
to get her betrothal gifts
for finding a wife for her brother.

31:43.280 --> 31:44.410
Now that I think about it,

31:44.760 --> 31:46.800
if Aunt Qin hadn't
gone through all this,

31:47.000 --> 31:49.000
perhaps she'd still be alive.

31:51.080 --> 31:53.450
If Qiao Beiyu hadn't
gone through all that,

31:54.130 --> 31:55.720
would she still be alive?

32:14.240 --> 32:16.000
I'm sorry. I've caused you trouble.

32:16.000 --> 32:17.320
We'll clean up the mess.

32:17.320 --> 32:18.800
Sorry. We're so sorry.

32:19.170 --> 32:20.610
Look at those scribbles.

32:21.130 --> 32:22.480
Qiao Beiyu?

32:24.170 --> 32:25.320
How many children are there
in their family?

32:25.760 --> 32:27.480
I think it's Qiao...

32:27.690 --> 32:28.560
Qingyu.

32:28.560 --> 32:29.240
Right.

32:29.240 --> 32:31.130
Yes, two of them.

32:37.170 --> 32:37.720
Oh my.

32:38.480 --> 32:39.410
Oh my.

32:40.370 --> 32:42.480
Who did this? This is terrible.

32:42.480 --> 32:43.450
Let me help you.

32:43.450 --> 32:44.520
No need.

32:45.040 --> 32:46.210
Thanks.

33:04.410 --> 33:05.850
Hey, here's mine. Sorry, I'm late.

33:06.040 --> 33:07.000
Hand it in earlier next time.

33:07.690 --> 33:09.080
Why are some still missing?

33:09.240 --> 33:10.890
Who hasn't submitted their homework?

33:12.610 --> 33:13.320
Where's she?

33:13.970 --> 33:15.760
No idea. It was like this
when I got here.

33:17.000 --> 33:18.560
She's probably hiding
because she didn't do her homework.

33:20.800 --> 33:22.760
Ming Sheng, turn in your homework.

34:20.080 --> 34:21.080
Why are you sitting here?

34:22.000 --> 34:22.650
The class is starting.

34:35.760 --> 34:38.239
I heard about what happened
to your shop.

34:39.480 --> 34:40.760
I thought it was something serious.

34:41.650 --> 34:42.449
It's no big deal.

34:43.130 --> 34:44.929
It's just some gossiping.

34:46.449 --> 34:47.520
Huanzhou is a big city,

34:47.800 --> 34:49.170
and many things happen every day.

34:49.889 --> 34:51.370
They'll forget a few days later.

34:55.000 --> 34:56.560
Do you think Qiao Beiyu

34:56.800 --> 34:58.560
was just as upset as I am now?

35:01.170 --> 35:01.850
No.

35:03.520 --> 35:04.850
She must've felt even more terrible.

35:06.210 --> 35:08.890
Infinitely worse, or even beyond that.

35:11.000 --> 35:13.040
Actually, I used to hate Qiao Beiyu.

35:13.650 --> 35:15.760
I thought she was foolish and weak.

35:16.370 --> 35:18.370
She dragged our family into trouble
even after her death.

35:18.520 --> 35:19.970
But now I understand.

35:21.370 --> 35:22.720
Some wounds

35:22.850 --> 35:24.450
never heal up.

35:24.690 --> 35:25.970
She was too upset

35:26.170 --> 35:27.930
to handle it.

35:28.240 --> 35:30.280
That's why she chose to end her life,

35:30.280 --> 35:31.450
to escape the harshness of reality.

35:33.680 --> 35:34.770
But I'm not fine with it.

35:36.330 --> 35:37.970
She paid the ultimate price

35:37.970 --> 35:39.000
for her decision,

35:39.000 --> 35:40.080
while her tormentors

35:40.080 --> 35:41.600
faced no consequences.

35:43.290 --> 35:45.160
Is there really such a thing as justice?

36:03.680 --> 36:05.290
Can anyone solve this question?

36:06.080 --> 36:06.970
Well, it's fine.

36:06.970 --> 36:08.480
Let's continue working on this.

36:08.480 --> 36:11.160
We're looking at the absolute value
of F1 multiplied by F2.

36:11.600 --> 36:12.810
Does anyone

36:12.810 --> 36:14.040
have any questions so far?

36:14.850 --> 36:16.560
Note that MF1 equals 2,

36:16.560 --> 36:18.680
which is half the value

36:18.680 --> 36:20.000
of F1 times F2.

36:20.000 --> 36:21.890
It's evident

36:21.890 --> 36:23.600
that there are two

36:23.730 --> 36:24.970
because this is the origin point,

36:24.970 --> 36:26.600
which is our zero coordinate.

36:27.600 --> 36:30.160
Hey, you there.
No running in the hallway.

36:30.520 --> 36:31.450
All right, sir.

36:35.480 --> 36:38.250
It takes two hours to take the bus
to the city stadium.

36:38.930 --> 36:40.080
Why can't we take a cab?

36:40.250 --> 36:41.600
Stop acting like a baby.

36:42.200 --> 36:44.080
It'd cost a lot for all of us
to take cabs.

36:44.080 --> 36:44.810
Besides,

36:44.810 --> 36:46.680
we've got time before the match starts.

36:48.410 --> 36:49.520
But I'm not fine with it.

36:51.040 --> 36:52.680
She paid the ultimate price

36:52.680 --> 36:53.770
for her decision,

36:54.000 --> 36:55.040
while her tormentors

36:55.040 --> 36:56.640
faced no consequences.

36:57.600 --> 36:58.480
The bus is here.

37:02.250 --> 37:02.930
What's on your mind?

37:09.680 --> 37:11.450
Everyone gets one. Don't lose it.

37:11.450 --> 37:12.770
Tie it on your head.

37:13.290 --> 37:15.200
Have you memorized the new slogan?

37:15.330 --> 37:16.480
Yeah.

37:16.730 --> 37:18.770
When I shout, "Ming Sheng, Ming Sheng."

37:18.890 --> 37:20.290
You go

37:20.680 --> 37:23.290
- "Huanzhou High School wins!"
- "Huanzhou High School wins!"

37:23.290 --> 37:24.520
Yes, we know.

37:24.520 --> 37:26.640
You've made us practice this
countless times.

37:26.640 --> 37:29.560
Today's the finals. It's crucial.

37:30.000 --> 37:31.450
Don't mess up.

37:32.250 --> 37:32.810
All right.

37:34.000 --> 37:35.930
I heard No. 1 High School
sent a strong team.

37:35.930 --> 37:37.370
A few of them are sports students.

37:38.080 --> 37:40.640
We have nothing to fear.
With Ming Sheng's participation,

37:40.890 --> 37:42.410
victory is assured.

37:42.480 --> 37:44.890
For sure. The champion is ours.

37:44.890 --> 37:45.410
That's right.

37:45.410 --> 37:46.560
Yes, that's right.

37:49.370 --> 37:50.520
Who are you looking for?

37:51.040 --> 37:52.850
Is Qiao Qingyu from this class?

37:54.890 --> 37:56.250
Qiao Qingyu, someone's looking for you.

37:57.200 --> 37:58.290
It's not me.

37:58.410 --> 37:59.770
It's her boyfriend.

37:59.770 --> 38:01.730
Her boyfriend is waiting for her
at the gate.

38:05.850 --> 38:07.000
Dad, Mom, have some tea.

38:08.930 --> 38:10.810
You didn't tell us

38:10.890 --> 38:12.600
that you've been with him
for three years.

38:12.970 --> 38:14.640
Your relationship has been
kept a secret all this time.

38:14.640 --> 38:16.080
What exactly is Ming Qiuxin up to?

38:16.370 --> 38:17.600
Is he toying with you?

38:18.040 --> 38:18.890
Well.

38:19.480 --> 38:20.810
They're in love.

38:21.520 --> 38:22.890
How is that toying with her, then?

38:23.930 --> 38:24.770
Let me ask you this.

38:25.120 --> 38:26.600
When are you planning to get married?

38:30.200 --> 38:30.810
Mom.

38:32.770 --> 38:34.120
I don't have plans for that.

38:35.040 --> 38:36.640
Is it your idea or his?

38:40.120 --> 38:41.000
Enough.

38:41.560 --> 38:43.370
He's agreed to meet with us.

38:44.040 --> 38:45.160
That shows his sincerity.

38:45.370 --> 38:46.640
When you see Dr. Ming later,

38:46.930 --> 38:47.850
be nice to him.

38:48.120 --> 38:50.000
If not, you'll scare him off.

38:50.680 --> 38:51.040
Jeez.

38:51.040 --> 38:52.410
Of course, I know.

38:52.640 --> 38:54.810
I only nag in front of you.

38:56.120 --> 38:57.730
All right. Have some tea.

39:02.810 --> 39:03.410
Who's causing trouble here?

39:03.600 --> 39:05.120
What makes you think
we're causing trouble?

39:05.730 --> 39:06.480
Listen.

39:06.810 --> 39:08.120
These are students.

39:08.640 --> 39:10.410
They're different from the likes of you.

39:10.410 --> 39:12.000
That sounds interesting.

39:12.120 --> 39:13.080
What kind of people are we?

39:13.080 --> 39:13.770
Say it clearly.

39:14.000 --> 39:14.930
Qiao Qingyu is here.

39:15.890 --> 39:16.810
Qiao Qingyu.

39:17.450 --> 39:19.480
Qiao Qingyu is Hei's girl.

39:20.480 --> 39:21.290
Qingyu,

39:22.080 --> 39:23.520
I bought it from your parents' shop.

39:24.890 --> 39:25.560
It's delicious.

39:26.040 --> 39:27.640
Why don't you eat at her parents' shop?

39:29.640 --> 39:30.640
What exactly do you want?

39:36.000 --> 39:36.970
I've made up my mind.

39:38.040 --> 39:38.930
I want to ask you out.

39:39.040 --> 39:39.600
I'm not interested.

39:40.450 --> 39:41.160
If you don't listen to me,

39:41.160 --> 39:42.330
I'll make trouble for your family.

39:47.930 --> 39:49.450
Your sister used my money.

39:49.450 --> 39:50.200
She owed me.

39:50.640 --> 39:51.770
Now that she is dead,

39:51.770 --> 39:52.640
you have to pay it back.

39:54.770 --> 39:56.120
What about what you did to Qiao Beiyu?

39:57.290 --> 39:58.640
Are you actually jealous of her?

40:00.730 --> 40:03.480
Turns out she's jealous of her sister.

40:03.970 --> 40:04.560
It's fine.

40:05.000 --> 40:06.410
Even though you're not as pretty as her,

40:06.410 --> 40:07.250
I like it

40:07.250 --> 40:08.480
when you pretend
as if you were a decent girl.

40:08.730 --> 40:09.600
You have no idea what she was like...

40:09.600 --> 40:10.410
Shut up.

40:10.970 --> 40:11.770
I'm saying it anyway.

40:12.080 --> 40:13.520
You have no idea
what she was like, do you?

40:13.930 --> 40:15.040
Especially when she was drunk.

40:15.640 --> 40:17.000
She would do everything I told her to.

40:17.000 --> 40:17.560
Let go of me!

40:22.160 --> 40:22.850
She's got a knife!

40:59.250 --> 41:02.940
♪Perhaps♪

41:03.450 --> 41:09.150
♪The more we care,
the more careful we become♪

41:10.290 --> 41:15.690
♪Counting the distance
that separates us♪

41:16.690 --> 41:22.250
♪A single step,
and we'd be closer still♪

41:27.920 --> 41:31.590
♪In the future♪

41:32.050 --> 41:37.770
♪Time will reveal this secret♪

41:39.270 --> 41:44.340
♪Waiting is a silent promise♪

41:45.590 --> 41:50.750
♪That never expires♪

41:54.350 --> 41:58.820
♪Turns out that what's on my mind♪

41:59.820 --> 42:03.490
♪Is your name♪

42:03.990 --> 42:09.090
♪The only stubbornness in my heart♪

42:10.170 --> 42:13.390
♪At first sight♪

42:13.820 --> 42:17.100
♪The future has been determined♪

42:17.790 --> 42:23.350
♪Dreams began to feel real♪

42:24.450 --> 42:27.990
♪Turns out that what's on your mind♪

42:28.450 --> 42:32.390
♪Is a place♪

42:32.690 --> 42:38.250
♪Where the same story is held dear♪

42:38.920 --> 42:42.290
♪Fortunately, I'm not sensible enough♪

42:42.620 --> 42:46.090
♪Courage wasn't late too♪

42:46.620 --> 42:52.690
♪Only then does time not betray
our acquaintance♪
